Alexandra López, nke a maara dịka Alex Lopez bụ onye Naijiria na Brazil na-eme ihe nkiri na onye bubu ome ejiji  nlereanya, onye a maara nke ọma maka ọrụ ya dị ka nwanyị na-edina nwanyị na ihe nkiri mkparitauka nke Zeb Ejiro 1996.bụ Domitila II
N'afọ 1993, ọ bụ onye nke abụọ na asọmpi ngosi mma a ma ama, Most Beautiful Girl in Nigeria

A mụrụ López, onye Afro-Brazilian, na Nigerian agbụrụ(Igbo), na Jos ma zụọ ya na Obosi, Anambra steeti na ndịda ọwụwa anyanwụ Nigeria. Ọ bụ nwa nke abụọ sitere na ezinụlọ nwere ụmụ nwanyị ise na otu nwa nwoke.
López pụtara na Faruk Lasaki's Changing Faces ebe ọ na-egosipụta akparamagwa dị ka Franca, nwunye nke Naijiria  nke Dale, onye owuwu ụlọ ọcha

O meela ihe nkiri Nollywood dị ka Domitilla, Love, Sex & Marriage, Dangerous Girls, Abuja Connection 2&3, Emotional Hazard, The One I Love, Akata, Catastrophe, Jungle Justice, Moving Train, Remarkable Pains, Scout, Sisters On the Run, Six Problem Girls, The Good The Bad And The Terrible na Walls Have Ears
O mere nwanyị na-edina nwanyị n ibe ya na  ihe nkiri Zeb Ejiro bụ Domitilla
N'ihi agbụrụ o si abụghị, a na-akpọkarị ya "onye na-eme ihe nkiri Nollywood nke dị iche".
Ka ọ na-erule afọ 2011, Lopez alụghị di ma nwee nwa nwoke. N'ọnwa Julaị afọ 2013, a kọrọ na López na Slim Burna, onye na-agụ egwu na Port Harcourt na Naijiria, na-akpa
Ha abụọ zara na ha bụ naanị enyi.
